    "body": "Hello @0fatih \r\n\r\nThe current error is indeed a temporary measure before we transition to custom errors. In this case, we will want a custom error with arguments \r\n```\r\nerror MissingRole(address account, bytes32 role);\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis will come soon, but we want to make sure the tooling for handling errors is ready (it clearly wasn't when the feature was introduced in 0.8.4)",
